author: Desiree Murphy ET Online
title: Rita Ora is dating Blink-182's Travis Barker
text:
Travis Barker has a brand new beat, and we're not talking about one on his drum set.
The 39-year-old musician, best known as the drummer of rock band Blink-182 , is now dating British singer Rita Ora, a rep for Barker confirms to ET.
News: Rita Ora talks about breakup with Calvin Harris The new couple met only a week ago at the Power 106 All Stars Game at the Galen Center in Los Angeles on Sept. 20. A source says that Barker "really likes Rita."
"They're really into each other and have been hanging out since they met," the source reveals.
A day after the game, Barker took to Instagram to share a photo of the two, snapped by photographer Willie Toledo.
"Me and the beautiful @ritaora at @power_106 #Power106AllStars," Barker captioned the photo.
Ora reposted the pic on her own Instagram, writing, "Nice to see you too."

The 24-year-old singer wore a black and white cheerleader outfit to the event, hosted by the Los Angeles-based hip hop station.
"Today Ima be your cheerleader @Power106LA coz we can!!! #bodyonme," she tweeted, with a pic of her wearing the uniform. The back of the crop top was embroidered with the title of her new hit single, "Body On Me," featuring Chris Brown.

Ora recently split from her boyfriend of over a year, Tommy Hilfiger's son, Ricky Hilfiger, in July. Ora was also previously linked to Calvin Harris in June and Rob Kardashian in 2012.
